<http://example.org/inst/SocialMention_0087fe26f2e2691dea2dac10738dc45b> a asoft:SocialMention ;
    asoft:detectedSlangTopic "Heavy BBs" ;
    asoft:rawComment "**u/User_5589_Snipe:** Refs are so dumb. Passed chrono at 350 in the morning. Put my 0.36g pearls in for the woodland game and suddenly my Wolverine rig is 'shooting too hot' and 'creeping'. Like dude, it's basic physics. Air volume pushes heavier BBs more efficiently. Now my gat is zip-tied and my dwell is lowered. Rentals ruin everything." ;
    asoft:userCallsign "User_5589_Snipe" .

<http://example.org/inst/SocialMention_00ef110c3051dd9524c383c8e62afe28> a asoft:SocialMention ;
    asoft:detectedSlangTopic "Gearbox Failure" ;
    asoft:rawComment "**@User_1181_BB:** I swear the factory Tokyo Marui assemblers are deaf. My AK74U sounded like a screeching cat today. Mid-game it just locked up. Pulled the gearbox and the gears are absolute glitter. Motor was burning up because the AOE was trash. Gotta rebuild the whole train now." ;
    asoft:userCallsign "User_1181_BB" .

